  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Which are the top ninja dragon games?",
  "response": "Ninja dragon games combine the thrilling elements of ninja stealth and action with the fantastical aspects of dragons. Here are some of the top ninja dragon games across various platforms:\n\n### 1. **Ninja Gaiden: Dragon Sword**\n   - **Platform:** Nintendo DS\n   - **Description:** This action-packed game features Ryu Hayabusa, a legendary ninja, battling against demonic forces. The \"Dragon Sword\" in the title refers to Ryu's iconic weapon. The game is known for its fast-paced combat and challenging gameplay.\n\n### 2. **Shadow of the Ninja**\n   - **Platform:** Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, PC\n   - **Description:** While not directly featuring dragons, this game's dark, atmospheric world and ninja action have a mystical feel that resonates with dragon-themed settings. Players control two ninjas in a cooperative mission to save the world.\n\n### 3. **Dragon Quest XI: Echoes of an Elusive Age**\n   - **Platform:** PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, PC\n   - **Description:** This JRPG features a vast world with ninja characters and mythical dragons. The game offers deep storytelling and a mix of turn-based combat and exploration, making it a top choice for fans of both ninjas and dragons.\n\n### 4. **Ninja Dragon VR**\n   - **Platform:** VR Platforms (e.g., Oculus Quest, HTC Vive)\n   - **Description:** This virtual reality game allows players to experience the thrill of being a ninja battling dragons in immersive environments. It's a unique blend of action and fantasy, taking full advantage of VR technology.\n\n### 5. **Ni no Kuni II: Revenant Kingdom**\n   - **Platform:** PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, PC\n   - **Description:** This enchanting RPG features a world filled with magic, including ninja characters and majestic dragons. The game combines kingdom-building elements with an engaging story and beautiful visuals.\n\n### 6. **The Legend of Zelda: Skyward Sword HD**\n   - **Platform:** Nintendo Switch\n   - **Description:** While primarily known for its protagonist Link, this game includes elements of ninja-like combat and a significant dragon presence in its storyline and gameplay. The remastered HD version enhances the experience.\n\nThese games offer a range of experiences, from intense action to deep storytelling, all featuring ninja and dragon elements. Enjoy exploring these top titles!",
